<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />
    <title>Settings</title>
    <!--     Fonts and Font Awesome Icons     -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300,400,600,700" rel="stylesheet" />
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/b1baf8bd8e.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <!-- CSS Files -->
    <link id="pagestyle" href="../assets/css/soft-ui-dashboard.css?v=1.0.6" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>

  <body class="bg-gray-100">
    <main class="main-content position-relative max-height-vh-100 h-100 border-radius-lg">
      <div class="container-fluid py-2">
        <div class="row mb-2">
          <div class="col-xl-6 col-md-6 mb-2">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-body p-3">
                <h4>마케팅 DB</h4>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-xl-6 col-md-6 mb-2">
                    <div class="card">
                      <div class="card-body p-3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                          <h6 class="card-title">1. 마케팅 정보 업데이트</h6>
                          <p class="card-text">마케팅 데이터 시트 작성 후 클릭</p>
                          <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" id="marketing">Update</button>
                          </div>
                          <div id="marketing-alert"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-xl-6 col-md-6 mb-2">
                    <div class="card">
                      <div class="card-body p-3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                          <h6 class="card-title">2. 공통마케팅 및 물류비 배부</h6>
                          <p class="card-text">마케팅비 및 물류비 배부</p>
                          <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                            <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" id="allocate-expense">Allocation</button>
                          </div>
                          <div id="allocate-expense-alert"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-xl-6 col-md-6 mb-2">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-body p-3">
                <h4>매입자가 원가 DB</h4>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-xl-6 col-md-6 mb-2">
                    <div class="card">
                      <div class="card-body p-3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                          <h6 class="card-title">1. 미등록 원가 확인</h6>
                          <p class="card-text">매입자가 원가 데이터 시트에서 원가 작성</p>
                          <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                            <button class="btn btn-warning" type="button" id="cost">Check</button>
                          </div>
                          <div id="cost-alert"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-xl-6 col-md-6 mb-2">
                    <div class="card">
                      <div class="card-body p-3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                          <h6 class="card-title">2. 원가 정보 업데이트</h6>
                          <p class="card-text">원가 데이터 DB 업로드</p>
                          <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                            <button class="btn btn-warning" type="button" id="update-cost">Update</button>
                          </div>
                          <div id="update-cost-alert"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mb-2">
          <div class="col-xl-12">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-body p-3">
                <h4>국내 공통 정보 DB</h4>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-xl-3">
                    <div class="card">
                      <div class="card-body p-3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                          <h6 class="card-title">1. 국내 공통정보 업데이트</h6>
                          <p class="card-text">국내 정보 데이터 시트 작성 후 클릭</p>
                          <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                            <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="button" id="korea-infomation">Update</button>
                          </div>
                          <div id="korea-infomation-alert"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-xl-3">
                    <div class="card">
                      <div class="card-body p-3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                          <h6 class="card-title">2. 월별 합계 정보 업데이트</h6>
                          <p class="card-text">월별 합계 DB 업데이트</p>
                          <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                            <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="button" id="korea-month-infomation">Update</button>
                          </div>
                          <div id="korea-month-infomation-alert"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-xl-3">
                    <div class="card">
                      <div class="card-body p-3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                          <h6 class="card-title">3. 일별 합계 정보 업데이트</h6>
                          <p class="card-text">일별 합계 DB 업데이트</p>
                          <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                            <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="button" id="korea-day-infomation">Update</button>
                          </div>
                          <div id="korea-day-infomation-alert"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-xl-3">
                    <div class="card">
                      <div class="card-body p-3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                          <h6 class="card-title">4. 마케팅파트 정보 업데이트</h6>
                          <p class="card-text">마케팅 파트 정보 작성 후 클릭</p>
                          <div class="d-grid gap-2">
                            <button class="btn btn-secondary" type="button" id="marketing-part">Update</button>
                          </div>
                          <div id="marketing-part-alert"></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <!--   Core JS Files   -->
    <script src="../controls/settings.js" type="module" defer></script>
    <script src="../assets/js/core/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../assets/js/core/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../assets/js/plugins/perfect-scrollbar.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../assets/js/plugins/smooth-scrollbar.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/luxon@3.2.1/build/global/luxon.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
